设置定时器，移除定时器

Object.freeze()



background

background-size

background-size: cover | contain | 值

background-repeat

background-repeat: repeatRule || repeatRule1, repeatRule2, ...
repeatRule: repeat(单值语法) || repeat repeat(双值语法)

repeat    -> repeat repeat
repeat-x  -> repeat no-repeat
repeat-y  -> no-repeat repeat
space     -> space space
round     -> round round
no-repeat -> no-repeat no-repeat

repeat 按背景图设定的大小，重复，超出裁剪
space 按背景图设定的大小，重复，适应外部div宽高，不会裁剪
round 拉伸背景图大小，重复，适应外部div宽高，不会裁剪
no-repeat 不重复